import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0):
    v0 = jnp.cos(x0)
    v1 = jnp.tanh(x0)
    v2 = jnp.maximum(v1, x0)
    v3 = jnp.subtract(v0, v1)
    v4 = jnp.cos(v3)
    v5 = jnp.tanh(v2)
    v6 = jnp.multiply(v5, v1)
    v7 = jnp.subtract(v0, v3)
    v8 = jnp.subtract(v0, v1)
    return v8
